This patch moves pr_info() so that it is called without
rtp->cbs_gbl_lock locked.

Signed-off-by: Shigeru Yoshida <syoshida@redhat.com>
Tested-by: "Zhang, Qiang1" <qiang1.zhang@intel.com>
